import React from "react";

const ShopIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="43"
      height="43"
      viewBox="0 0 43 43"
    >
      <g id="Groupe_13" data-name="Groupe 13" transform="translate(-94 -176)">
        <rect
          id="Rectangle_12"
          data-name="Rectangle 12"
          width="43"
          height="43"
          transform="translate(94 176)"
          fill="rgba(255,255,255,0)"
        />
        <g
          id="Icon_feather-shopping-cart"
          data-name="Icon feather-shopping-cart"
          transform="translate(105.5 187.5)"
        >
          <path
            id="Tracé_12"
            data-name="Tracé 12"
            d="M13.5,30.783A.751.751,0,1,1,12.751,30,.768.768,0,0,1,13.5,30.783Z"
            transform="translate(-5.245 -13.616)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
          <path
            id="Tracé_13"
            data-name="Tracé 13"
            d="M30,30.783A.751.751,0,1,1,29.251,30,.768.768,0,0,1,30,30.783Z"
            transform="translate(-13.486 -13.616)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
          <path
            id="Tracé_14"
            data-name="Tracé 14"
            d="M1.5,1.5h3L6.515,11.989a1.518,1.518,0,0,0,1.5,1.261h7.3a1.518,1.518,0,0,0,1.5-1.261l1.2-6.573H5.254"
            transform="translate(0 0)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default ShopIcon;
